   Netmask Examples (Based Around IPv4 Class C Network)
   ────────────────────────────────────────────────────

      Netmask 255.255.0.0 or /16    :   2^16 Hosts - 65,536 Hosts Per Network (256 Class C Network - 1 Class B Network)
      Netmask 255.255.128.0 or /17  :   2^15 Hosts - 32,768 Hosts Per Network (128 Class C Network)
      Netmask 255.255.192.0 or /18  :   2^14 Hosts - 16,384 Hosts Per Network (64 Class C Network)
      Netmask 255.255.224.0 or /19  :   2^13 Hosts -  8,192 Hosts Per Network (32 Class C Network)
      Netmask 255.255.240.0 or /20  :   2^12 Hosts -  4,096 Hosts Per Network (16 Class C Network)
      Netmask 255.255.248.0 or /21  :   2^11 Hosts -  2,048 Hosts Per Network (8 Class C Network)
      Netmask 255.255.252.0 or /22  :   2^10 Hosts -  1,024 Hosts Per Network (4 Class C Network)


      Netmask 255.255.254.0 or /23  :   2^9  Hosts -    512 Hosts Per Network (2 Class C Network)
      -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
      Network                0
      Hosts       [0.1 - 1.254]
      Broadcast          1.255


      Netmask 255.255.255.0 or /24  :   2^8  Hosts -    256 Hosts Per Network (1 Class C Network)
      -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
      Network                0
      Hosts           [1 - 254]
      Broadcast            255


      Netmask 255.255.255.128 or /25:   2^7  Hosts -    128 Hosts Per Network (1/2 Class C Network)
      -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
      Network                0 ,         128
      Hosts           [1 - 126],  [129 - 254]
      Broadcast            127 ,         255


      Netmask 255.255.255.192 or /26:   2^6  Hosts -     64 Hosts Per Network (1/4 Class C Network)
      -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
      Network                0 ,          64 ,         128 ,         192
      Hosts            [1 - 62],   [65 - 126],  [129 - 190],  [193 - 254]
      Broadcast             63 ,         127 ,         191 ,         255


      Netmask 255.255.255.224 or /27:   2^5  Hosts -   32 Hosts Per Network (1/8 Class C Network)
      -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
      Network                0 ,          32 ,          64 ,          96,          128 ,         160 ,         192 ,         224
      Hosts            [1 - 30],    [33 - 62],    [65 - 94],   [97 - 126],  [129 - 158],  [161 - 190],  [193 - 222],  [225 - 254]
      Broadcast             31 ,          63 ,          95 ,         127 ,         159 ,         191 ,         223 ,         255


      Netmask 255.255.255.240 or /28:   2^4  Hosts -     16 Hosts Per Network (1/16 Class C Network)
      Netmask 255.255.255.248 or /29:   2^3  Hosts -      8 Hosts Per Network (1/32 Class C Network)
      Netmask 255.255.255.252 or /30:   2^2  Hosts -      4 Hosts Per Network (1/64 Class C Network)

